               <p>Third London Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
               <p>1476. 
               
                  <persName id="t18341016-2-defend147" type="defendantName">
                     BENJAMIN 
                     THORNLEY
                  <interp inst="t18341016-2-defend147" type="surname" value="THORNLEY"></interp>
